---
title: Greek-Inspired Breaded Chicken Breast with Garlic-Feta Cucumber Salad
description: Greek-spiced chicken, savoury roasted potato wedges and tzatziki sauce are the stars of this dinner. A side of garlic-feta cucumber salad rounds out this Mediterranean flavour feast!
